CMD_Element.name: channel
CMD_Element.Documentation: (primary channel) describes the medium or channel by which a text is delivered or experienced. For a written text, this might be print, manuscript, e-mail, etc.; for a spoken one, radio, telephone, face-to-face, etc. (source: http://www.tei-c.org/release/doc/tei-p5-doc/en/html/ref-channel.html)
